*Brinuće* se da svi budu zadovoljni (They will take care that everyone is satisfied). 

*Brinula* se za svoje dete (She was concerned about her child). 

*Brinu* se za svoje zdravlje (They are concerned about their health). 

*Brinuti* se oko stvari koje nisu važne nije od koristi (Caring about things that are not important is not useful). 

*Brinut će* se da se sve ispoštuje (They will take care that everything is respected).